{
  "stem": "11184.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 60.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 185,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On our coats, yeah, whatever we were wearing, we had to-- we could-- we could not go out without them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 186,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 187,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 187,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 188,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm-hmm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 189,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 190,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 191,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How difficult-- we had to find a little cart, a pushcart, you know, to put on all our belongings.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 191,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] You know, and we put them on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 191,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, and as I told you, my father tried to go into business himself.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 191,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He looked so forward--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 192,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--to, to, to make a better living for his family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 192,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he had those machines.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 192,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And those machines meant, like-- you know, that he cherished them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 193,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this had to be put on-- also on that cart--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 194,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--and [LAUGHS] pushed and pushed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 194,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we all pushed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 194,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Whatever we could, we, we took with us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 194,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were given a one-room apartment again, one room--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 195,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--one room in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 195,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Assigned-- we were assigned--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 196,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--to one room.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 197,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There-- it was that, that, that committee.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 197,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 198,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A Jewish committee was formed--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 199,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, uh-huh.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 199,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- yeah, because I think the Germans were in touch with the Jewish committee, so-- through them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 200,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Smaller.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 201,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a smaller one, yeah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 201,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was much smaller.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 202,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm-hmm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 202,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it's there where my grandmother passed away, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 203,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She just fell asleep.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 204,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 205,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "70, I think.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 206,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Uh-huh, uh-huh.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 207,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not so old.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 207,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hungry, hungry and--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 208,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 209,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't have enough.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 209,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there was still food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 209,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, there was still food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 209,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were complaining that this is not good and that is not good.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 209,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there was still some food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 210,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And systematically, it came to nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 210,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 211,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--it, it went-- it went systematically, so we, we got used to it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 211,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We're conditioned to it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 211,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So for some people, they could survive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 211,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And others couldn't survive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 212,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Others were falling.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
